{"id":152948,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国之声-意大利人将执掌欧洲央行/","date":"2011-05-17T23:30:27Z","modified":"2011-05-17T23:30:27Z","title":"德国之声 | 意大利人将执掌欧洲央行","content":"<div>\n<p>布鲁塞尔<br />意大利央行行长马里奥·德拉吉（Mario Draghi）出任欧洲央行行长的道路已经畅通。欧元区国家财长提名63岁的德拉吉接替现任欧洲央行行长特里谢（Jean-Claude Trichet），后者将在今年10月按规定结束任期。欧元集团主席容克在布鲁塞尔举行的相关会议上透露了这一消息。最终决定将在6月24日的欧盟峰会上做出。此前，欧元区财长决定向葡萄牙提供高达780亿欧元的紧急援助贷款。其中三分之一由国际货币基金组织提供。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15081751%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%86%E6%89%A7%E6%8E%8C%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}